headline: Bernstein issues a warning on U.S. auto stocks: The downgrade cycle isn’t over
summary: Investing.com -- Bernstein told investors in a note Wednesday not to be misled by strong second-quarter results in the U.S. auto sector, warning that a downturn looms in the second half of 2025 and into 2026.
